member.summary:
Static canvas node builder helpers.
All methods return  instances.



using Lpdf;
using Lpdf.Canvas;

var layer = LpdfCanvas.Layer([
    LpdfCanvas.Rect(0, 0, 595, 842, new RectStyle(Fill: "lightgray")),
    LpdfCanvas.Text(100, 100, "Hello"),
]);

Static document skeleton builder.
Produces , ,
, and  instances
for use with .



using Lpdf;
using Lpdf.Kit;
using Lpdf.Layout;

var doc = LpdfKit.Document(
    nodes: [
        LpdfKit.Section(
            nodes: [ LpdfKit.Layout([ LpdfLayout.Text(["Hello"]) ]) ],
            options: new SectionOptions(Size: "a4"))
    ]);

Static layout node builder helpers.
All methods return  instances.



using Lpdf;
using Lpdf.Layout;

var text = LpdfLayout.Text(["Hello"], new TextOptions(Font: "heading"));
var stack = LpdfLayout.Stack([text], new StackOptions(Gap: "m"));
